    <title>LaTeX数学公式</title>
    <link href="/2021/06/03/LaTeX%E7%BB%83%E4%B9%A0/"/>
    <url>/2021/06/03/LaTeX%E7%BB%83%E4%B9%A0/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>导数：</strong><br>$c{}’=0$<br>$x^{u}{}’=ux^{u-1} $<br>$(\frac{1}{x}){}’=-\frac{1}{x^{2}}$<br>$(\sqrt{x}){}’=\frac{1}{2\sqrt{x}}$<br>$(\frac{1}{\sqrt{x}}){}’=-\frac{1}{2}x^{-\frac{3}{2}}$<br>$(a^{x}){}’=a^{x}lna$<br>$(e^{x}){}’=e^{x}$<br>$(\log_{a}{x}){}’=\frac{1}{xlna}$<br>$(lnx){}’=\frac{1}{x}$<br>$sinx{}’=cosx$<br>$cos{}’=-sinx$<br>$tanx{}’=sec^{2}x$<br>$cotx{}’=-csc^{2}x$<br>$secx{}’=secxtanx$<br>$cscx{}’=-cscxcotx$<br>$arcsinx{}’=\frac{1}{\sqrt{1-x^{2}}}$<br>$arccosx{}’=-\frac{1}{\sqrt{1-x^{2}}}$<br>$acrtanx{}’=\frac{1}{1+x^{2}}$<br>$acrcotx{}’=-\frac{1}{1+x^{2}}$</p><p><strong>等价无穷小：</strong><br><img src="/img/blog/数学/高数/狗头.jpg" alt=""></p><p><strong>基本积分公式：</strong></p><p>$\int adx=ax+C$</p><p>$\int x^{u}dx= \frac{1}{u+1} x^{u+1} + C$</p><p>$\int \frac{1}{x}\mathrm{d}x= \ln \left| x \right| +C$</p><p>$\int \sqrt[]{x}dx=\frac{2}{3}x^{\frac{3}{2} }+C   $</p><p>$\int \frac{1}{\sqrt{x} } dx=2\sqrt[]{x} +C $</p><p>$\int \frac{1}{x^{2} }  dx=-\frac{1}{x}+C $</p><p>$\int a^{x}dx=\frac{1}{\ln a}a^{x} +C$</p><p>$\int e^{x}dx=e^{x}+C$</p><p>$\int sinxdx=-cosx+C$</p><p>$\int cosxdx=sinx +C$</p><p>$\int tanxdx=-\ln |cosx|+C$</p><p>$\int cscxdx=\ln |cscx-cotx|+C$</p><p>$\int secxdx=\ln |secx+tanx|+C$</p><p>$\int cotxdx=\ln |sinx|+C$</p><p>$\int sec^{2}xdx=tanx+C$</p><p>$\int csc^{2}xdx=-cotx+C$</p><p>$\int secxtanxdx=secx+C$</p><p>$\int cscxcotxdx=-cscx+C$</p><p>$\int \frac{1}{\sqrt{1-x^{2}} }dx=arcsinx+C $</p><p>$\int \frac{1}{\sqrt{a^{2}-x^{2}}}dx=arcsin\frac{x}{a}+C$</p><p>$\int \frac{1}{1+x^{2}}dx=arctanx+C$</p><p>$\int \frac{1}{a^{2}+x^{2}}dx = \frac{1}{a}arctan\frac{x}{a}+C$</p><p>$\int \frac{1}{x^{2}-a^{2}}dx=\frac{1}{2a} \ln |\frac{x-a}{x+a}|+C$</p><p>$\int \frac{1}{\sqrt{x^{2}\pm a^{2}}} dx = \ln| x + \sqrt{x^{2}\pm a^{2}} |+C$</p><p><strong>凑微分法:</strong><br>$\int \Box d \Box =\frac{1}{2}\Box^{2}+C$</p><p>$\int e^{\Box}d\Box=e^{\Box}+C$</p><p>$\int sin\Box d\Box=-cos\Box+C$</p><p>$\int cos\Box d\Box=sin\Box+C$</p><p>$\int \sqrt{\Box}d\Box=\frac{2}{3}\Box^{\frac{3}{2}}+C$</p><p>$\int \frac{1}{\Box}d\Box=ln|\Box|+C$</p><p>$\int \frac{1}{\sqrt{1-\Box^{2}}}d\Box$</p><p>$\int \Box^{u}d{\Box}=\frac{1}{u+1}\Box^{u+1}+C$</p><p>$\int \frac{1}{x^{2}-a^{2}}dx=\frac{1}{2a}ln|\frac{x-a}{x+a}|+C$</p>]]></content>
    
    
